v&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;cx_paywall_placeholder&quot; id=&quot;sph_cdp_40&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt; </description><link>https://www.zaobao.com/realtime/china/story20240813-4473766</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.zaobao.com/realtime/china/story20240813-4473766</guid><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 03:21:28 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>